snippet.title: [TAS] Intellivision Skiing "Downhill" in 33.8
snippet.description:
TAS notes: http://tasvideos.org/7156S.html
In-Game Time: 33.8
TAS time: 1:16.318

The primary goal is to minimize in-game time, as is performed in the first heat. Fun fact, it is only 0.2 seconds faster than the RTA world record. As a secondary goal, I reach the final screen while ending input as early as possible. This means Heat 2 focuses on fastest real time and Heat 3 on earliest input end.
